Know about branches:
git branch



push a branch to remote:
git push -u origin main

If fatal SSH error occurs:

git config --global http.sslBackend schannel
and then:
git push -u origin main

You need to authenticate the github account
and then check the repository for the updated content


Two ways to create a new branch:
1) Create and Switch to a New Branch
    git checkout -b feature-branch
2) Create Multiple Branches, but remain at the main branch
    git branch feature-login
    git branch feature-payment
Later go to the branch by 
    git checkout feature-branch

Delete a branch:
Delete Branches usually done after Merge
git branch -d feature-login

Step : Create the branch dev :
git checkout -b feature-dev

To see the branches:
 git branch


